---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="Medical Weight Loss Program in Dallas–Fort Worth | AymanCare"
  description="Physician-supervised weight loss with real medical support — not fad diets. Personalized plans at four Dallas–Fort Worth clinics."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
  <script type="application/ld+json" is:inline set:html={"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Services\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Weight Loss\",\"item\":\"https://aymancare.com/services/weight-loss/\"}]}"} />
  </Fragment>
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="breadcrumbs fade-in">
    <a href="/">Home</a><span class="sep">✦</span><a href="/services/">Services</a><span class="sep">✦</span><span>Weight Loss</span>
  </div>

  <div class="svc-hero">
    <div>
      <span class="svc-hero-badge fade-in"><span class="ic"></span>Medically supervised</span>
      <h1 class="page-title fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><em>Weight</em><br>loss.</h1>
      <p class="svc-hero-lede fade-in">Medically supervised weight loss programs focused on sustainable health — building the habits, physiology, and support system that make real change last.</p>
      <div class="svc-hero-chips fade-in"><span class="pill">Physician-guided</span><span class="pill pill-accent">Whole-person</span><span class="pill">Insurance options</span></div>
      <div class="svc-hero-ctas fade-in">
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book this visit →</a>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="svc-hero-visual fade-in">
      <img src="/images/weight-loss-hero.jpg" alt="Weight Loss">
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
  <div class="svc-main">
    <aside class="svc-aside">
      <div class="aside-card fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Service details</div>
        <h3>Our <em>approach</em></h3>
        <ul><li>Full health assessment</li><li>Lab work & metabolic panel</li><li>Nutrition guidance</li><li>Physical activity planning</li><li>Medication support</li><li>Ongoing follow-up</li></ul>
      </div>
      <div class="aside-card dark fade-in">
        <div class="l">✦ Ready to book?</div>
        <h3>Same-day <em>appointments</em> available.</h3>
        <a href="/contact/" class="big-num">View all locations →</a>
        <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 16px; margin-bottom: 20px;">Call or book online — walk-ins welcome at every location.</p>
        <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-accent" style="width: 100%; justify-content: center;">Book online →</a>
      </div>
    </aside>

    <div class="svc-content">
      <h2>More than a <em>number.</em></h2><p>Weight loss isn't just about a scale. It's about how you feel in your body, your energy, your sleep, your mood, and your long-term risk for conditions like diabetes, heart disease, and joint problems. Our program treats weight as one vital sign among many.</p><h2>What the <em>program</em> looks like.</h2><p>We start with a full health assessment — labs, history, lifestyle — and build a plan from there. That might include nutrition strategy, activity planning, medication support where appropriate, and ongoing check-ins so we can adjust the plan as your body changes.</p><blockquote>"The best weight loss plan is the one you can actually live with for the rest of your life."</blockquote><h2>Built to <em>last.</em></h2><p>We're not interested in quick fixes that leave you back where you started in six months. The goal is a sustainable approach that builds your body's health and improves your habits — so you can enjoy life, not just fit into a number.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="svc-grid-band">
  <div class="svc-grid-band-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ At a glance</span>
    <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">By the <em>numbers.</em></h2>
    <div class="three-col"><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Whole-person</div>
      <h4>Approach</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Physician</div>
      <h4>Supervised</h4>
    </div><div class="mini-card fade-in">
      <div class="num">Ongoing</div>
      <h4>Support</h4>
    </div></div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
<section class="related-services">
      <div class="section-header" style="margin-bottom: 0; padding-bottom: 0; border-bottom: none;">
        <div>
          <span class="overline fade-in" style="margin-bottom: 16px; display: block;">◆ Related services</span>
          <h2 class="section-title fade-in" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 48px);">Explore <em>more</em>.</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="related-grid"><a href="/services/primary-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Primary</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Long-term care and annual wellness — your family physician.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/walk-in-urgent-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Walk-In</em> Urgent</h4>
          <p>Same-day care for acute illness, injury, and COVID testing.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a><a href="/services/pediatric-care/" class="related-card fade-in">
          <h4><em>Pediatric</em> Care</h4>
          <p>Child-centered care from newborn to teen.</p>
          <span class="link">Learn more →</span>
        </a></div>
    </section>
</section>

<section class="big-cta">
  <div class="big-cta-inner">
    <span class="overline fade-in">◆ Ready when you are</span>
    <h2 class="fade-in">Let's take care<br>of <em>you.</em></h2>
    <p class="fade-in">Book online in under a minute, or walk into any of our four Dallas-area locations today.</p>
    <div class="cta-row fade-in">
      <a href="/book-online/" class="btn btn-primary">Book appointment →</a>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-outline">Call your nearest clinic</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
</Base>
